【表达式】:
	由变量、常量和运算符组成的公式称为表达式。


【操作符】:
	算术运算符:
        +   -   *   /   %   **  //
        addition    subtraction   multiplication   division   remainder   power   DivisionInteger
        Format: param1 Operator param2

	赋值运算符:
        =
        EqualSign
        Format: variables = expressions
        Composite Operators:
            +=  -=  *=  /=  %=  **=  //=
            Format: param1 Operator param2

	位运算符:
        &(按位与)      |(按位或)      ^(按位异或)   ~(按位取反)   <<(按位左移)   >>(按位右移)
        BitwiseAnd  BitwiseOr   BitwiseXor  BitwiseInvert
        Analys:
            &: The value in the corresponding position is the same,the result is 1,otherwise 0.
            |: There is a corresponding posistion where the value is 1 and the result is 1,otherwise 0.
            ^: The value in the corresponding position is the diffrence,the result is 1,otherwise 0.
            ~: The vlaues in corresponding positions are reversed.

	关系运算符:
        ==  !=  >   <   >=  <=

	逻辑运算符:
        and(逻辑与)    or(逻辑或)   not(逻辑非)
        LogicalAnd   LogicalOr    LogicalNot

	成员运算符:
        in      not in
        Analys:
            in: If the value is found in the specified sequence,retrun true,otherwise false.
            not in: If the value is not found in the specified sequence,return true,otherwise false.

    Identity Operators:
        is   is not
        Analys:
            is: Determines whether two identifiers refer to the same object.
            is not: Determines whether two identifiers refer to the different object.


【if语句】
    Format 1:
        if Expression:
            Statement

        For example:
            if 3 > 2:
                print("Yes")

        Analys:
            If the result of the expression is true, The program will execute the statement.Otherwise the program will not execute the statement.

    Format 2:
        if Expression:
            Statement 1
        else:
            Statement 2


























